{"tid":1771181,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要事業有成先結得婚？","createTime":"2019-12-05T16:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T14:10:01.000Z","uid":299479,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9edbb4e4dc921ed2411cf7b5bd6086b52697e935","tid":1771181,"uid":299479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"同男友一齊3年幾 <br />\n大家都係適婚年齡..都有plan會結婚<br />\n但佢事業仲係浮浮沉沉<br />\n成日都唔知自己想點咁，又話事業要穩定先結<br />\n我又睇唔到佢事業幾時先穩定<br />\n30歲幾人都仲係無乜發展方向<br />\n我又淨係識言語上鼓勵佢唔緊要，下次再努力<br />\n但其實我都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經由成日催逼佢到而家都唔想再提結婚<br />\n覺得講黎都晒氣 又開始嫌棄佢廢<br />\n我上黎求大家屌醒我<br />\n我仲想同依個人過人世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a140b17d6c687c3a18e7c28a6096ad8a0e280664","tid":1771181,"uid":50744,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"我諗佢係想同女人結婚"},{"pid":"39a12f0183ab1e9df46ddfe6b1a230bb6b125eb6","tid":1771181,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a140b17d6c687c3a18e7c28a6096ad8a0e280664","tid":1771181,"uid":50744,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"我諗佢係想同女人結婚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5c30c4e2e6bd3f7b3347f6386395c69a0355a4","tid":1771181,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"咁都要有錢先得架。。"},{"pid":"545d2f401184b018ef3f727104c37c5594bb16b9","tid":1771181,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"你自己事業有成<br />\n佢搶住娶你<br />\n當然到時你又有更多選擇"},{"pid":"53b9178e36a1e439134713a68d9521a020472471","tid":1771181,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"擺酒結婚所有費用你包九成，睇佢肯唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01eacdccda5fe85ce50e2e9c3769c53d94f66f7d","tid":1771181,"uid":299479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b9178e36a1e439134713a68d9521a020472471","tid":1771181,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"擺酒結婚所有費用你包九成，睇佢肯唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"其實我地都唔諗住擺酒"},{"pid":"b6a021ea196441dd25485da15b986f609c6062d8","tid":1771181,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登已經被入侵!!!星期六行動post冇人推，大家入黎同我推爆佢春袋!!!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hksuckagain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhksuckagain&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=e9889ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hksuckagain</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【緊急!!!連登冇人推行動post!!!】和理非12.7一齊遊車河塞春袋!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1771177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1771177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b474299b03d79c3e799069d40b2db08420bf6a6","tid":1771181,"uid":172035,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"有啲男仔咁諗<br />\n結婚 = 組織家庭 = 生兒育女 = 供書教學blablabla <br />\n所以喺佢哋角度，事業有成係結婚嘅必要條件<br />\n依份信心唔只係俾你同佢，仲有你哋嘅下一代，你哋嘅屋企人。<br />\n<br />\n但假如樓主主張活在當下，或者唔想生育嘅話<br />\n事業有成甚至算唔上結緍嘅充分條件添<br />\n咁就簡單得多，大家深入啲傾多幾傾，有共識就得啦。<br />\n<br />\n最弊嘅只會係如果雙方都覺得事業有成係必要條件，<br />\n而男方又得個大隻講，口話要事業有成，做又有心無力<br />\n咁做女仔嘅真係要認真諗諗，好唔好繼續聽佢呃呃氹氹啦"},{"pid":"a777ad8a0966f5cb5909e3b8923f45c8dfefa4f6","tid":1771181,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9edbb4e4dc921ed2411cf7b5bd6086b52697e935","tid":1771181,"uid":299479,"like":0,"dislik